ce" target="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01752">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, [17. 1. 1908]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01754">Kraus an Schnitzler, 20. 1. 1908</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01749">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 8. 1. 190[8?]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01758">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 25. 1. 1908</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
